title: How to draw animals

creator: True Fun Apps
descriptionHtml:
Love to draw? Do you want to learn how to learn to draw? Then this app is just for you!

How to Draw Animals - is a drawing game that will help you learn how to draw step by step.

The drawing app offers you a convenient way to draw: you can draw on paper, all you need is paper, pencil and eraser, or on your phone screen!

A clear and simple interface will help you easily draw a real masterpiece right on your phone screen!

How To Draw Animals - is not only a drawing game but also a colorful coloring book. You can repeat the color of the drawing, as the instruction pictures show, or come up with your own original version of the coloring of the animal.

Here are collected hundreds of bright pictures-tutorials on how to draw animals step by step in various styles from cartoonish kawaii chibi drawings to complex realistic portraits of animals. Here you can easily choose the level of difficulty that suits you.

Such drawing games are suitable for a wide range of users: for girls and boys, for beginners and professionals!

Our drawing game will introduce you to all the animals of our vast planet: the inhabitants of the safari, the cold Arctic, representatives of the underwater world, beautiful birds, interesting insects, animals living on the farm, and of course everyone's favourite cats and dogs!

You will get cool drawings of various animals: horse, panda, cat, dog, wolf, lion, sloth, unicorn, dinosaur, dragon and much more.

The drawing app works offline, without the Internet.

Download our drawing games right now and enjoy!
